at cri=\r\ncketer. But isn&#39;t Tendulkar also a father, brother, son, husband, a respons=\r\nible citizen of India, a consumer at the local grocery store, and for all y=\r\nou know maybe even a reasonable bathroom singer? These are all his identiti=\r\nes too. But why don&#39;t we refer to them when we speak of Tendulkar? Because =\r\nhis central defining identity for us is his cricket.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;spa=\r\nn&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;Same way, each deity eventually is everyth=\r\ning. But each has its own &quot;defining identity&quot; which has its own set of attr=\r\nibutes. Of all the people worshipping Lalita Tripursundari at this very mom=\r\nent, probably a 2 percent or less&nbsp;will realize Her in this lifetime. O=\r\nf these, 99.9999999999999999999 percent will realize Her ONLY in Her&nbsp;c=\r\nhief identity as Lalita. How many will, or have till date, actually realize=\r\nd that form of Lalita Tripursundari sitting on a pretasana? And why is this=\r\n form&nbsp;so remote and so uncommon for most standard worshippers of Lalit=\r\na Tripursundari? These are questions to ponder!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/s=\r\npan&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;I&#39;ve very little=\r\n knowledge of worship of Sri Lalita Tripursundari, either theoritical or fr=\r\nom the point of practical worship,&nbsp;but if there is beauty in this worl=\r\nd, it is Her.&nbsp;Like a five course gourmet&nbsp;meal, like a sublime poe=\r\ntry, like&nbsp;an efforlessly brilliant music, like a dazzling play of ligh=\r\nts, like a classic Tendulkar shot,.... all these combined together and much=\r\n much&nbsp;more ...you feel and wish that it never comes to an end. It is d=\r\nifficult to describe the feeling that She evokes, but it&#39;s like a flood of =\r\npure, distilled essence of&nbsp;beauty and you feel like there is nothing m=\r\nore to be done, no goal to reach, no path to walk, no battles to fight -&nb=\r\nsp;simply bask in the depth of the moment because therein lies fullfilment =\r\nand a whole new world! She banishes the very roots of the sense of strife a=\r\nnd ugliness from your system... the knowledge that She exists is enough to =\r\nincapacitate you from asking anything\n more. She is THE greatest&nbsp;poetr=\r\ny of all possible Universes of all possible cycles of creation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div=\r\n&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;=\r\n-Regards&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;Rajarshi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;b&gt;=\r\n&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY:Verdana;COLOR:navy;FONT-SIZE:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=\r\n=3D&quot;#000000&quot; face=3D&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;COLOR:rgb(0,0,102);=\r\n&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#a2a2a2&quot; size=3D&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/font=\r\n&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;var&gt;&lt;/var&gt;&=\r\nnbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY:times new roman, new york, times, ser=\r\nif;FONT-SIZE:12pt;&quot;&gt;\n&lt;div style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY:times new roman, new york, t=\r\nimes, serif;FONT-SIZE:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=3D&quot;Arial&quot;&gt;\n&lt;div style=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE:=\r\n0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-WEIGHT:bold;&quot;&gt;From:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; Srikanth =\r\n&lt;&lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; ymailto=3D&quot;mailto:srikanthnetworked@...&quot; targ=\r\net=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;mailto:srikanthnetworked@...&quot;&gt;srikanthnetworked=\r\n@...&lt;/a&gt;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-WEIGHT:bold;&quot;&gt;To